      <abstract>
        <p>Patent attorney Mark Levy letter holds photo of Rube Goldberg cereal-preparation apparatus should have been included in June 4 article on young scientists at Midwood High /// 55 NYT 07 02 00 0006 00008 4 38 I LR 975044 THE SMART SET***Patent attorney Mark Levy holds photo of Rube Goldberg cereal-preparation apparatus should have been included in June 4 article on young scientists at Midwood High0</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>After reading your provocative description of the Rube Goldberg cereal-preparation apparatus, ''Breakfast for One,'' my fellow patent attorneys and I shall never forgive you for neglecting to include a photograph of the inventors' prototype.</p>
        <p>Mark Levy  Binghamton, N.Y.</p>
      </block>
